{"tid":95295,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[激流] 連人帶浴缸遭龍捲風吹走 大命女缸內安全「着陸」","createTime":"2017-01-26T02:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T02:05:59.000Z","uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2baead8ce49fa9ca0b7b32c13bd22fa6dc9f4eaf","tid":95295,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170125/280pix/1485339562_c706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170125%2F280pix%2F1485339562_c706.jpg&h=e6dc656c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56221256&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56221256%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170126&d=dzXL1%2FGw5IWxb47Be3Ujhn8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=e09c95ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56221256%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170126&h=b0fda9a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56221256&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170126</a><br />\n<br />\n美國南部日前受雷暴侵襲，造成19人死亡，德州更出現龍捲風，一名女子躲在浴缸內，浴缸被龍捲風捲起並拋到鄰近叢林，「着陸」她仍藏身浴缸內，奇蹟生還並僅受輕傷，十分神奇。<br />\n<br />\n美國國家氣象局（National Weather Service）指，周六的龍捲風闊731米（800碼），風速達每小時209公里，龍捲風捲走不少建築物頂部，當中包括一名年約60多歲女子的住所。<br />\n<br />\n氣象學家漢斯福德（Jason Hansford）指，「她聽到龍捲風警告，她躲在廁所的浴缸中。她只記得龍捲風來自西南邊，橫越她的屋，屋子的後半部份被扯走。她的浴缸被吹走，最後她仍在浴缸內，落在住所附近的叢林」。<br />\n<br />\n漢斯福德不清楚女事主被捲走有多遠，但指她僅割傷和瘀傷，「她沒有（嚴重）受傷，但情緒有點波動」。<br />\n<br />\n氣象網站Accuweather指，浴室結構較堅固，牆有水管有助對抗龍捲風，而浴缸緊緊連接地下，大多數能抵擋龍捲風，因此不少專家都建議，一旦龍捲風來襲，居民最好匿在浴缸內避難。"},{"pid":"346e8330fa3a010fc9aadee13585e99d3e9d8fee","tid":95295,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:04:46.000Z","msg":"仲以為佢沖沖下涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb1601b0bfc91a6fed9248b65bca1860406176a","tid":95295,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}